This is how to fizz_buzz of n:
  When remainder of n and 15 is 0, then:
    The answer is 0
  End when
  When remainder of n and 3 is 0, then:
    The answer is 2
  End when
  When remainder of n and 5 is 0, then:
    The answer is 1
  End when
  The answer is 3
